Package com.ab.exceptions

A package containing custom exceptions used in this framework

See: Description

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ExcelFileNotFoundException
    The ExcelFileNotFoundException class extends the InvalidFilePathException class to represent an exception that occurs when the Excel file is not found at the specified path.
    ExcelReadException
    The ExcelReadException class extends the FrameworkExceptions class to represent an exception that occurs when an error occurs while reading an Excel file.
    FrameworkExceptions
    The FrameworkExceptions class extends the RuntimeException class to represent exceptions that occur in the framework.
    InvalidFilePathException
    The InvalidFilePathException class extends the FrameworkExceptions class to represent an exception that occurs when an invalid file path is provided.
    PropertyNotFoundException
    The PropertyNotFoundException class extends the FrameworkExceptions class to represent an exception that occurs when a property is not found.
